00:51:39,862 --> 00:51:42,839
Michal! Michal!

661
00:51:43,864 --> 00:51:45,576
Persetan ini.

662
00:51:46,104 --> 00:51:48,215
Aku selesai dengan
bualan psikopat ini.

663
00:51:51,004 --> 00:51:52,359
Aku melihat Charlie.

664
00:51:52,384 --> 00:51:53,829
